
INSTALL:

1. Download Linux Kernel Source Code, and go to "security" directory.
2. Put the whole "lsm" directory under "security" directory.
3. Replace the Kconfig file and Makefile File under "security" directory.
4. Type "make menuconfig", and Un-check the modules using LSM (e.g. SMACK, SELinux, AppArmor). Make sure the added "lsm" module is selected.
5. Compile and install the kernel.
6. Reboot.